	; doc: @param RSP  array  by-ref response: 200 text/html, the whole console in one page
"RTN","VWEBT",167,0)
	; A thin route over a hand-rolled page (the one place hand-written HTML/JS is OK —
"RTN","VWEBT",168,0)
